  m_Name: Chief Prologue Dialogue 3
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  Lines:
  - charName: Chief Vandham
    line: Now that you two are here, I have a special request from both of you.
    reaction: 
    choices: []
    redirectDialogueIndex: -1
  - charName: Fiona
    line: Oh! A special request from the chief?
    reaction: 
    choices: []
    redirectDialogueIndex: -1
  - charName: Chief Vandham
    line: The nearby forest has been quite overridden with wild slimes lately.
    reaction: 
    choices: []
    redirectDialogueIndex: -1
  - charName: Chief Vandham
    line: With how many roaming around the area, it'll threaten the safety of our
      village.
    reaction: 
    choices: []
    redirectDialogueIndex: -1
  - charName: Chief Vandham
    line: I want you two to work together to take them all out.
    reaction: 
    choices: []
    redirectDialogueIndex: -1
  - charName: Fiona
    line: Really chief, are you sure? Why ask us?
    reaction: 
    choices: []
    redirectDialogueIndex: -1
  - charName: Chief Vandham
    line: You two have shown me your strength and the way you fight. I see potential
      in both of you.
    reaction: 
    choices: []
    redirectDialogueIndex: -1
  - charName: Chief Vandham
    line: Think of it as a training exercise.
    reaction: 
    choices: []
    redirectDialogueIndex: -1
